name: Prophesied Kings of the Egg
description: Hailing from the high reaches of Mt. Kalfus, the Prophesied Kings of the Egg mentioned in goatlich’s prophecy foretelling the end of days. Now finally living a life of leisure as their ‘investments’ grow their wealth beyond imagining, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
